<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/marcus-bell> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Marcus Bell is Director of the Office for Equality and Opportunity in Cabinet Office, having been Director of the Race Disparity Unit since 2016. Marcus is a career civil servant, with a background mainly in social policy. He previously worked in the Department for Education, Ministry of Justice, and Ministry of Housing, Communities & Local Government. Marcus was awarded the OBE for public service in the 2023 New Year’s Honours List ."@en .
